s Tears)\" by [[Wendy Rene]], written by Joseph W. Frierson and [[Wendy Rene|Mary Lou Frierson]].\n*\"7 Rings\" interpolates portions of \"[[My Favorite Things (song)|My Favorite Things]]\", written by [[Oscar Hammerstein II]] and [[Richard Rodgers]].\n*\"Break Up with Your Girlfriend, I'm Bored\" contains an interpolation of \"[[No Strings Attached (NSYNC album)|It Makes Me Ill]]\" by [[NSYNC]].\n\n==Personnel==\nCredits adapted from [[Tidal (service)|Tidal]] and the album's [[liner notes]].<ref name=\"linernotes\">{{Cite AV media notes |title=Thank U, Next |others=[[Ariana Grande]] |year=2019 |type=CD booklet |publisher=[[Republic Records]] |id=602377175011|page=1\u20137}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://listen.tidal.com/album/103692735|title=''Thank U, Next'' by Ariana Grande|last=|first=|date=|website=[[Tidal (service)|Tidal]]|accessdate=February 8, 2019}}</ref>\n\n===Vocals===\n{{div col}}\n* [[Ariana Grande]] \u2013 primary artist\n* [[Victoria Mon\u00e9t]] \u2013 background vocals {{small|(tracks 2\u20133, 7\u20138, 10\u201311)}}\n* [[Tayla Parx]] \u2013 background vocals {{small|(tracks 2\u20133, 7, 10)}}\n* Marjorie Grande \u2013 background vocals {{small|(track 4)}}\n* Doug Middlebrook \u2013 background vocals {{small|(track 9)}}\n* [[Shangela|Shangela Laquifa Wadley]] \u2013 uncredited vocals {{small|(track 3)}}<ref>{{citeweb|title=Shangela 'Thrilled' to Be on Ariana Grande's 'Thank U, Next' Album: 'You Gotta Be Kidding'|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/pride/8497354/shangela-ariana-grande-album-nasa|date=February 8, 2019}}</ref>\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Instrumentation===\n{{div col}}\n* Happy Perez \u2013 guitar {{small|(tracks 1, 5, 9)}}, keyboards {{small|(tracks 1, 5, 9)}}\n* [[Pop Wansel]] \u2013 keyboards {{small|(tracks 1, 5, 9)}}\n* Peter Lee Johnson \u2013 strings {{small|(track 2)}}\n* Wojtek Bylund \u2013 [[alto saxophone]] {{small|(track 4)}}\n* [[Ilya Salmanzadeh]] \u2013 bass {{small|(tracks 4, 6, 8, 12)}}, drums {{small|(tracks 4